OL,3,CGas engineers on site after tragic
OL,4,Cdeaths of mum and son in Rochdale
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after a
OL,7,Fman in his 60s was found dead at a
OL,8,Fhouse in Greater Manchester and a
OL,9,Fwoman at property - thought to be his
OL,10,Fmother - passed away in hospital a
OL,11,Fshort time later.
OL,13,FNeighbours reported the sound of a
OL,14,Fbang coming from the house on Foxholes
OL,15,FRoad in Rochdale just after 5pm on
OL,16,FFriday (27 December).
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,19,FService confirmed it attended the
OL,20,Fscene between 6pm and 8pm, before
OL,21,Fhanding over to police.
