OL,4,Cdeaths of mum and son in Rochdale
OL,6,FThere are not thought to be any
OL,7,Fsuspicious circumstances surrounding
OL,8,Fthe deaths.
OL,10,FA GMP spokesman said: "At around
OL,11,F5.10pm on Friday, December 27 2024, we
OL,12,Fwere called to reports of a concern
OL,13,Ffor welfare on Foxholes Road in
OL,14,FRochdale. Sadly, a man in his 60s was
OL,15,Ffound dead at the scene and a woman in
OL,16,Fher 80s later died in hospital.
OL,18,F"There are not believed to be any
OL,19,Fsuspicious circumstances surrounding
OL,20,Ftheir deaths. Investigations are
OL,21,Fongoing."
