OL,3,CGas engineers on site after tragic
OL,4,Cdeaths of mum and son in Rochdale
OL,6,FA spokesman for Cadent said: "I can
OL,7,Fconfirm that Cadent engineers attended
OL,8,Fa property in Foxholes Road last night
OL,9,Fin support a multi-agency response.
OL,11,F"We now know that two people have died
OL,12,Fand, on behalf of everyone at Cadent,
OL,13,FI offer our sincere condolences to
OL,14,Ftheir family and friends.
OL,16,F"As the region's gas emergency
OL,17,Fservice, it is routine in an incident
OL,18,Fof this nature for Cadent to be asked
OL,19,Fto check everything associated with
OL,20,Fgas is safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
