OL,3,CGas engineers on site after tragic
OL,4,Cdeaths of mum and son in Rochdale
OL,6,F"We did this and left about 45 minutes
OL,7,Fafter our arrival at the address.
OL,9,F"The cause of death will be
OL,10,Finvestigated by other agencies. If
OL,11,Fanyone ever smells gas, or suspects
OL,12,Fthe presence of carbon monoxide, act
OL,13,Fimmediately and call the gas emergency
OL,14,Fservice on 0800 111 999. All calls are
OL,15,Frecorded and may be monitored."
