OL,3,CGas engineers on site after tragic
OL,4,Cdeaths of mum and son in Rochdale
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,7,FFire and Rescue Service (GMFRS) said:
OL,8,F"At just before 6.15pm on Friday
OL,9,F(December 27) three fire engines from
OL,10,FRochdale and Littleborough fire
OL,11,Fstations were called by Greater
OL,12,FManchester Police (GMP) reports of a
OL,13,Fconcern for welfare on Foxholes Road
OL,14,Fin Rochdale.
OL,16,F"Firefighters worked alongside
OL,17,Fcolleagues from North West Ambulance
OL,18,FService and Cadent Gas to make the
OL,19,Fscene and surrounding area safe. Crews
OL,20,Fwere in attendance for around one hour
OL,21,Fand 45 minutes."
